articles.title: Mark Butcher: ‘No matter what happens at The Oval, England will look back on this series as a lost opportunity | Ashes 2023 - Wisden
articles.description: England will look back on the Ashes series as a "lost opportunity" according to Mark Butcher, despite putting in a performance at Old Trafford which could have represented "the peak of Bazball".
